    • Method Detail

      • getAdvanceParams

        public static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> getAdvanceParams()
        Get a HashMap containing parameters that is used to connect to a firebird database a non-default way.
        Usage: .put with new value overriding old one.

        Parameters (defaults in parentheses):
        COLUMNLABELFORNAME, Boolean(True)
        ENCODING, String(UTF8)
        USER, String(SYSDBA)
        PASSWORD, String(masterkey)
        HOST, String(localhost:3050) (host:port)

        Returns:
        HashMap with parameters
